@env.head(2,'Test 1')
The Universal Program Driver, flx_run,
runs a Felix program with no inputs.
This driver is located in flx_rtl.ipk.
@p()
This routine just loops through
numbers 1 to 10, and prints if they're odd or even.

@select(env.test('.flx'))
